Ok, de-lvling I can understand.  That's a pretty filthy exploit.  But changing X-teaming?  Don't do that!  X-teaming allows people to make alliances outside their team.  It allows people to play within the framework of the teams idea but still gives them room to maneuver.  I play both light and dark characters.  I enjoy my dark being on only one team.  But my light character groups with everyone.  The majority of my friends are on different teams.  It'd ruin Tallon Zek for me.
