This is to Rale Dragonsblade:<P>That would be cool to stop all the lame low level pking that you may experience, but what about all the high lvl guild wars and such that go on?  And what if you see a hurt Darkenbane in the zone....does your faction answer give you low faction for killing him if he attacks you?  Or what if you just kill him and he doesn't touch you?  If they did implement faction it should only be for the town itself and the newbie areas surrounding it.  Basically it would only work in any zone that has guards of that town.  The guards would hear about your murderous rampage and be mad at you.  Maybe they could even make it super agro so any guard within a mile radius would run at the pker.  And in the case of adding faction for your hometown..that should only work if you kill another race in your own town or newbie area.  Otherwise how would the guards hear about it?  This would make it so that newbies could hunt in newbie areas without being killed by de-lvled jerks but it would also make it so darkelves could defend their home against the light invaders. <P>Just my 2 cents<BR>Moffon Furryhealer<BR>52 Vicar - Rallos Zek
