X-Teaming<P>I have been reading on this Topic and want to make a comment. Think in a Roleplaying mind here for a minute. From time's Beginning people have been good or bad. Right, Right. Since times beginning people have been converted from good to bad or bad to good. Right, Right. This applies to the game also with Darks and Lights. People will convert from dark to light and light to dark. Don't touch or penalize this. It is hueman and Roleplaying Nature. This is a good thing if you think about this for 2 seconds. People get mad and say they should stop it, This is because that are in the ROLEPLAYING MINDSET. They are upset because they feel betrayed. THis is what Roleplaying is and how it is supposed to be. Think, Roleplaying allows you to take your character and develop a persona. If I want to make a ranger, and become an EVIL Ranger, then so be it. Nothing wrong with that. THere is an Old Saying, "You Make your Bed, You can Lay in It." There is alot of truth to that statement. If Everyone thinks on this that reads this youw ill see the logic and make sence out of it. Thats my 2 CP Worth.
