<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
   So far it has been pretty unanimous about de-leveling.  No sense in wasting time on that.<P>   Also seems unanimous to leave x-teaming alone as well.  I agree as well.  However, I do think a few things need to be changed on the PVP servers, that no one has mentioned fully yet.<P>   Make the servers like the others, you can only be attacked by someone within four levels of you.  One to two levels lower or higher, blue, yellow.  Three levels lower or higher and beyond, green, red.<P>   Now for the part that will help make sense to this.  Allowing x-teaming, nothing above a six level spread can affect a target character.   Either benificial or not with spell buffs.  This will eliminate the problem of having ubber Healers so much, but still allow for some cool "buffs" from a higher up.<P>   Don't treat the PVP servers the same as the other servers so much,  Take some time to code in more changes that make sense to PVP.  Such as, you can not attack a player that has killed you for a set amount of time.  Not that you do not get your HT or LoH back.  That is sort of lame.<P>   Faction affects the "buffer" in a PK situation the same as it does the Killer.  When you attack a mob and someone heals you, they gain/loose faction based upon the kill same as you.  Make it the same for Pking,  That way if x-teaming is involved, they also get the bad faction hit.<P>   I also play light and dark characters, only on TZ, only server I have ever played on.  I use my light Cleric, and roleplay his religion, which is Innoruuk.  I buff only DE and other Darks, I only Heal DE and other darks, and chastise other lights for inturupting while they attack me.  I understand I am a target for my "chosen" friends, most of them kill me a few times before they give up when I run back and buff them again.  But very few other Light races bother to attack me.  I like roleplaying him that way, and will continue to do so.<P>   Anyways, Do good by the players with the changes, or don't bother to make changes at all, you have already messed it up for us enough already.<P>Strost Shadowdreamer<BR>Shadowknight Incarnate<BR>Tallon Zek
</FONT>
